Introduction

    This plugin for Maven provides an wrapper around the SchemaExport class of 
    Hibernate 4. Using parameters it is possible to configure the plugin from 
    the POM. This plugin requires Java 7 and Maven 3.

    The goals of this plugin are described at the Goals page. The Usage page
    provides informations about how the plugin is used.


